description: Jean-Luc is a student just trying to survive. He's got a delicious swimmer's body and a shy demeanor that makes me want to make it rain! I gotta thank the chill in the air today that makes Jean-Luc eager to come back to my hotel room where he can be more comfortable. From that point on it was inevitable that I would get up in those lean swimmer guts and shoot a hot load all over him.
title: Jean-Luc
